  "body": "Hi there,\r\n\r\n2 contracts, Called and Test, And 1 private chain with geth's version 1.8.20. I only deployed the Test, and Called is newed by Test(See code for detail).\r\nThe question is, when i call setHello(\"Hello World\") at Test, it's all OK, but after that, when i call getHello(), get empty string. But in Called, getHello() returns \"Hello World\".\r\n\r\nAll steps:\r\n    In Test:\r\n    1. setHello(\"Hello World\") -> Success\r\n    **2. getHello() -> Sucess, but returns empty string** (Why ???)\r\n    3. getCallAddress() -> Success, get the Called's address\r\n    So, In Called:\r\n    4. getHello() -> Success, and returns \"Hello World\"\r\n\r\n**I am use [Remix](http://remix.ethereum.org) for test.\r\nUse Ropsten is OK. Only with problem in private chain.**\r\n\r\n```\r\npragma solidity 0.5.3;\r\n\r\ninterface ICall {\r\n    function setHello(string calldata _hello) external;\r\n    function getHello() external view returns (string memory);\r\n    function setI(uint256 _i) external;\r\n    function getI() external view returns (uint256);\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract Called is ICall {\r\n    string public hello;\r\n\r\n    uint256 public i;\r\n\r\n    function setHello(string calldata _hello) external {\r\n        hello = _hello;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function getHello() public view returns (string memory) {\r\n        return hello;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function setI(uint256 _i) external {\r\n        i = _i;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function getI() external view returns (uint256) {\r\n        return i;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract Test {\r\n    string strHello;\r\n\r\n    ICall public called = new Called();\r\n\r\n    uint256 constant BASE_MASK = uint256(uint128(~0)) << 128;       // highest 128 bits for Base Type;\r\n    uint256 constant NFT_INDEX_MASK = uint256(uint64(~0)) << 64;\r\n    uint256 constant FT_INDEX_MASK = uint256(uint64(~0));\r\n\r\n    uint256 public iTest = 30;\r\n\r\n    event LogSetHello(address indexed owner, string hello);\r\n    event LogSetI(address indexed onwer, uint256 i);\r\n    \r\n    function getCallAddress() public view returns (address) {\r\n        return address(called);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function getHello() public view returns (string memory _helloTmp) {\r\n        _helloTmp = called.getHello();\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function setHello(string calldata _hello) external {\r\n        called.setHello(_hello);\r\n\r\n        emit LogSetHello(msg.sender, _hello);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```",
